sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Applicant as 入党申请人/管理角色
  participant H5 as 服务号 H5
  participant API as Node API
  participant Auth as 认证/权限守卫
  participant DB as MySQL
  actor Organizer as 组织员/管理员

  Applicant->>H5: 首次注册(name/idNo/employeeNo/password)
  H5->>API: POST /api/auth/register
  API->>DB: 查询预置 users.username = employeeNo
  alt 预置人员不存在
    API-->>H5: 400 后台未找到预置人员信息
  else 预置人员存在
    API->>DB: 写入 registration_requests(pending)
    API->>DB: 记录审计日志
    API-->>H5: 已提交，等待审核
  end

  Organizer->>API: POST /api/auth/approve-registration
  API->>Auth: requireAuth + requirePermission(approve_registration)
  Auth-->>API: 已登录且有审批权限
  API->>DB: 读取注册申请和目标用户范围字段
  API->>Auth: canAccessScopedRecord(审批人, 申请人)
  alt 无权限或跨范围
    API-->>Organizer: 403
  else pending 且范围覆盖
    API->>DB: 更新申请 status=approved/rejected
    opt approved
      API->>DB: 激活 users.status=active
      API->>DB: 确保 applicant 角色
    end
    API->>DB: 记录 approve_registration 审计
    API-->>Organizer: 审批完成
  end
